description: ndependently owned and pathologist operated full-service reference laboratory. We provide pathology services to doctors' offices, federally qualified health centers, health departments, family planning clinics, and hospitals throughout the United States. Additionally, we provide reference pathology services to various regional laboratories. We offer a variety of services including Pap smear screening, molecular pathology, non-gynecologic cytology, surgical pathology, clinical lab testing and more. As an independently owned and pathologist directed laboratory, we are flexible enough to serve your needs while maintaining an exceedingly high quality. When working with us, there is no “box” your business needs to fit in. Rather, our goal is to build a process that fits your organization and your patients’ health care needs. This approach to laboratory services gives our clients the confidence in the service they receive through the relationships forged in the process. Most laboratories have call centers located off-site from operations, which makes adding tests, or making changes difficult.
